  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test a method for analyzing interactions between patients and
      doctors, the Roter Interaction Analysis System (RIAS). The RIAS measures the quality of
      communication between patients and their cancer doctors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
