  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>study-specific coding structure</measure>
    <time_frame>2 years</time_frame>
    <description>using the RIAS in cancer care across English and Spanish languages will be assessed by evaluating whether this existing, validated coding system 'works' across a language barrier.</description>
